5 (צִיר) in the sense of ambassador;","strongs_def":"to make an errand, i.e. betake oneself","kjv_def":"make as if...had been ambassador.","pos":"verb","usage":"ambassador(1x)"},"H6738":{"id":"H6738","lemma":"צֵל","translit":"tsêl","pron":"tsale","derivation":"from H6751 (צָלַל);","strongs_def":"shade, whether literal or figurative","kjv_def":"defence, shade(-ow).","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"shadow(45x), defence(3x), shade(1x)"},"H6739":{"id":"H6739","lemma":"צְלָא","translit":"tsᵉlâʼ","pron":"tsel-aw'","derivation":"(Aramaic) probably corresponding to H6760 (צָלַע) in the sense of bowing;","strongs_def":"pray","kjv_def":"pray.","pos":"verb","usage":"pray(2x)"},"H6740":{"id":"H6740","lemma":"צָלָה","translit":"tsâlâh","pron":"tsaw-law'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to roast","kjv_def":"roast.","pos":"verb","usage":"roast(3x)"},"H6741":{"id":"H6741","lemma":"צִלָּה","translit":"Tsillâh","pron":"tsil-law'","derivation":"feminine of H6738 (צֵל);","strongs_def":"Tsillah, an antediluvian woman","kjv_def":"Zillah.","pos":"proper feminine noun","usage":"Zillah(3x)"},"H6742":{"id":"H6742","lemma":"צְלוּל","translit":"tsᵉlûwl","pron":"tsel-ool'","derivation":"from H6749 (צָלַל) in the sense of rolling;","strongs_def":"a (round or flattened) cake","kjv_def":"cake.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"cake(1x), variant(1x)"},"H6743":{"id":"H6743","lemma":"צָלַח","translit":"tsâlach","pron":"tsaw-lakh'","derivation":"or צָלֵחַ; a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to push forward, in various senses (literal or figurative, transitive or intransitive)","kjv_def":"break out, come (mightily), go over, be good, be meet, be profitable, (cause to, effect, make to, send) prosper(-ity, -ous, -ously).","pos":"verb","usage":"prosper(44x), come(6x), prosperous(5x), effected(1x), good(1x), meet(1x)"},"H6744":{"id":"H6744","lemma":"צְלַח","translit":"tsᵉlach","pron":"tsel-akh'","derivation":"(Aramaic) corresponding to H6743 (צָלַח);","strongs_def":"to advance (transitive or 